description: Creates a Vector Enrichment job for the supplied job type. Currently, there are two supported job types: reverse geocoding and map matching.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: A unique token that guarantees that the call to this API is idempotent. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: ExecutionRoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role that you specified for the job.

parameters.name: InputConfig
parameters.description: Input configuration information for the Vector Enrichment job. The input structure for the data source that represents the storage type of the input data objects. S3Data (dict) --- The input structure for the Amazon S3 data that represents the Amazon S3 location of the input data objects. KmsKeyId (string) --- The Key Management Service key ID for server-side encryption. The URL to the Amazon S3 data for the Vector Enrichment job. The input structure that defines the data source file type.
